text:
What?
Somehow I have a bad feeling about this.

It's a lizard!
Don't you have some pets like this, Mamimi-chan?

Well, I do have some pets like this but
my pets are a bit different from this one.

That right?
But aren't they from the same family or something?

Anyway that one in the river there,
isn't that a newt?

Alright,
I'll try to catch that then!
What are you going to do if you catch it?

I'll give it you,
of course!
